 Nótese que 
\begin_inset Formula ${\displaystyle \frac{\partial}{\partial\dot{q}_{u}}\left(\sum_{j=1}^{n}\frac{\partial\vec{r}_{i}}{\partial q_{j}}\dot{q}_{j}\right)=\frac{\partial\vec{r}_{i}}{\partial q_{u}}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
A continuación, tenemos:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
