Sean 
\begin_inset Formula $n\in\mathbb{N}$
\end_inset

 e 
\begin_inset Formula $y\left(t\right):I\subseteq\mathbb{R}\longrightarrow\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

 una función de clase 
\begin_inset Formula $C^{\left(n\right)}$
\end_inset

.
