=\left[\frac{2KZq_{e}^{2}}{mv^{2}}\right]^{2}\frac{1}{2\sin^{2}\frac{\theta}{2}}\frac{\overbrace{\frac{1}{2}\sin^{2}\frac{\theta}{2}+\frac{1}{2}\cos^{2}\frac{\theta}{2}}^{=\frac{1}{2}}}{\sin^{2}\frac{\theta}{2}}=\left[\frac{2KZq_{e}^{2}}{mv^{2}}\right]\frac{1}{4\sin^{4}\frac{\theta}{2}}=\left[\frac{2KZq_{e}^{2}}{2mv^{2}\sin^{2}\frac{\theta}{2}}\right]^{2}=
\]

