\[
T_{2,f}=\frac{4p^{*\,2}\sin^{2}\frac{\theta^{*}}{2}}{2m_{2}}=\frac{2p^{*\,2}}{m_{2}}\sin^{2}\frac{\theta^{*}}{2}
