=-GM_{L}\rho dV\left[\left(\frac{1}{R^{2}\left(1+\frac{y^{2}}{R^{2}}\right)^{\frac{3}{2}}}-\frac{1}{R^{2}}\right)\hat{i}+\frac{y}{R^{3}}\hat{j}\right]
\]

